Connection Guide:-

ESP8266 NodeMCU Connections:

3.3V → IR Sensor VCC, LEDs through resistors

3.3V → Ultrasonic Sensor VCC

GND → All components GND

Ultrasonic Sensor:

TRIG → D1 (GPIO5)

ECHO → D2 (GPIO4)

IR Sensor:

OUT → D5 (GPIO14)

LEDs:

Red LED anode → D6 (GPIO12) through 220Ω resistor

Green LED anode → D7 (GPIO13) through 220Ω resistor

Both cathodes → GND
